*<div id="function.ibase-free-result" class="refentry">  <div class="refnamediv">   <h1 class="refname">ibase_free_result</h1>   <p class="verinfo">(PHP 5, PHP 7)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">ibase_free_result</span> &mdash; <span class="dc-title">Free a result set</span></p>   </div>    <div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-function.ibase-free-result-description">   <h3 class="title">说明</h3>   <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description">    <span class="type">bool</span> <span class="methodname"><strong>ibase_free_result</strong></span>     ( <span class="methodparam"><span class="type">resource</span> <code class="parameter">$result_identifier</code></span>    )</div>    <p class="para rdfs-comment">    Frees a result set.   </p>  </div>    <div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.ibase-free-result-parameters">   <h3 class="title">参数</h3>   <p class="para">    <dl>            <dt> <code class="parameter">result_identifier</code></dt>       <dd>        <p class="para">        A result set created by <span class="function">{@link ibase_query()}</span> or        <span class="function">{@link ibase_execute()}</span>.       </p>      </dd>          </dl>    </p>  </div>    <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.ibase-free-result-returnvalues">   <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>   <p class="para">    成功时返回 <strong><code>TRUE</code></strong>， 或者在失败时返回 <strong><code>FALSE</code></strong>。   </p>  </div>   <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.ibase.php">Firebird/InterBase 函数</a></div></div>
