ter">len</code> bytes from the BLOB, or <strong><code>FALSE</code></strong>    on failure.   </p>  </div>    <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.ibase-blob-get-examples">   <h3 class="title">范例</h3>   <p class="para">    <div class="example" id="example-1190">     <p><strong>Example #1 <span class="function"><strong>ibase_blob_get()</strong></span> example</strong></p>     <div class="example-contents"> <div class="phpcode"><code><span style="color: #000000"> <span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br />$result&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">ibase_query</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"SELECT&nbsp;blob_value&nbsp;FROM&nbsp;table"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$data&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">ibase_fetch_object</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$result</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$blob_data&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">ibase_blob_info</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$data</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">BLOB_VALUE</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$blob_hndl&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">ibase_blob_open</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$data</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">BLOB_VALUE</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br />echo&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">ibase_blob_get</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$blob_hndl</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$blob_data</span><span style="color: #007700">[</span><span style="color: #9876AA">0</span><span style="color: #007700">]);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span> </span> </code></div>     </div>     </div>    Whilst this example doesn&#039;t do much more than a    &#039;ibase_blob_echo($data-&gt;BLOB_VALUE)&#039; would do, it does show you how to get    information into a $variable to manipulate as you please.    </p>  </div>    <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.ibase-blob-get-seealso">   <h3 class="title">参见</h3>   <p class="para">    <ul class="simplelist">     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link ibase_blob_open()} - Open blob for retrieving data parts</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link ibase_blob_close()} - Close blob</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link ibase_blob_echo()} - Output blob contents to browser</span></li>    </ul>   </p>  </div>   <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.ibase.php">Firebird/InterBase 函数</a></div></div>
